---
title: Mushroom and Chickpea Fajitas with tomato salsa and cooling creme fraiche
description: The best thing about these veggie fajitas—aside from the taste—is how easily they come together. Ready in less than 30 minutes, and served in a DIY style, this is the ultimate easy breezy recipe.
